# Cursor Rules

1. Read all the rules in this file before you start working on any task.
1. Any content you need to create, documentation, test scripts, etc. should be stored in the AI-generated-content-not-for-git directory. If appropriate, create sub directories in AI-generated-content-not-for-git.
2. Do not commit any content from the AI-generated-content-not-for-git directory to the repository.
3. The user will move any AI-generated-content-not-for-git into appropriate locations and commit it themeselves
4. If asked for a commit message, keep it to 1 sentance



